    <string name="about_pocra_details">Maharashtras Project On Climate Resilient Agriculture (POCRA) is a constructive effort to develop in farmers the skills to adapt to the changing climate patterns. The results of the efforts made through the Nanaji Deshmukh Krishi Sanjeevani project (POCRA) are being visible. The last few years have seen major changes in the climate. Agriculture and climate are closely related. The project is designed keeping in mind that climate has great impact on agriculture and to enhance the profitability of farmers despite the climate change.</string>

